---
title: Herby Beef Meatballs & Garden Salad with Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: For beef meatballs with some Mediterranean vibes, lace them with our rich herb seasoning. Then add an extra layer of flavour by
coating them in our onion chutney before serving over a simple and textural salad to balance out the richness. Don't forget the
drizzle of creamy basil pesto dressing to tie everything together.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

*Due to local availability, we’ve replaced some of your ingredients. They may be a little different to what’s pictured, but just as delicious!*
